WEBVTT

00:01:28.211 --> 00:01:30.714
Tears are now flowing down her face.

00:01:31.252 --> 00:01:34.733
And in response,
Grandmother Jack moves closer,

00:01:35.375 --> 00:01:37.329
puts her hand on Farai,

00:01:37.353 --> 00:01:40.538
and says, "Farai, it's OK to cry.

00:01:41.800 --> 00:01:43.257
You've been through a lot.

00:01:44.453 --> 00:01:46.401
Would you like to share more with me?"

00:01:47.060 --> 00:01:48.747
And Farai continues.

00:01:50.140 --> 00:01:51.841
"In the last three weeks,

00:01:52.666 --> 00:01:56.413
I have had recurrent thoughts
of killing myself,

00:01:57.603 --> 00:01:59.608
taking my two children with me.